item.description:
We've reserved space at the Exeter library to host what will be the first-ever SeaL Candidate Action Meetup. Those who are interested in volunteering to help fellow SeaLs running for public office are encouraged to attend!

We have the library space available for an hour and a half and if necessary will move the gathering to a nearby venue TBD.

See you there!
item.name: Seacoast Liberty Candidate Action Meetup
